; --- WELL-HEAD hero landmark (S1-YARD T8, Uma s1-yard-ground-composition.md §3.1).
; South-central, OFF the processional spine at the south route-choice decision
; point, ringed by a worn slab apron (painted by the script) — a wonder-landmark +
; NPC-station seed the player is drawn toward. Collision-solid (WellBody, built by
; the painter) so it's a walk-AROUND structure.
; SOAK-REVISION (#426, Sponsor 2026-06-08): the well was "WAY out of proportion —
; drastically too big (~5-6x the player)". Scale 0.85→0.35 so the rim DIAMETER reads
; ~1.5x the char_scale=0.6 player HEIGHT (in-context measure: well rendered ~81px wide
; vs player ~54px tall = 1.5x), a real well a person draws from — calibrated to the
; HUMAN-SCALE fountain in inspiration/2026-06-08_07h53_24.png (art-direction.md §3),
; NOT a building (spec §3.1 target). Footprint dropped 3x3→2x2 to match the smaller
; solid base. z=2 (Props, above floor/buildings). Recentred to tile (21,17) ≈ the new
; 2x2 footprint centre so the painted apron still rings it.
[node name="WellHead" type="Sprite2D" parent="Props"]
position = Vector2(672, 544)
scale = Vector2(0.35, 0.35)
texture = ExtResource("8_well")
